Edit the files standard.phml, editing.phtml and viewing.phtml in layouts.

Add 1 <div id="bg"> around the whole content of <body> to the 3 layouts:

<body>
<div id="bg">
...
</div>
</body>

Change $theme in includes/config.inc to 'mountain':

$theme='mountain';

